Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Swine flu outbreak
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z99j1
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 28 Mar 1976
President Ford backs plan to vaccinate entire US population against swine flu outbreak. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less